Data abstraction
	1.It is used to provide the relevant information to the user and hide	
	  the irrelevant information from the user
	or
	2.it is used to provide necessary information to the user and hide
	  the unnecessary information from the user
	e.g Console.WriteLine();
		//hides all the complexility inside this one
Data Encapsulation
	1.It is used to group the related data together and hide the complexity
	  and provide the security to the data/information
	2.E.g Class

